<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<!-- TemplateBeginEditable name="doctitle" -->
<title>Rent A Pet Home Page</title>
<!-- TemplateEndEditable -->
<link href="../mystyles.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css">
<script type="text/javascript" src="../myscripts.js"></script>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="print.css" media="print">
<!-- TemplateBeginEditable name="head" -->
<!-- TemplateEndEditable -->
</head>

<body onload="preloadImages()">

<div id="container">

    <header>
    	<img src="../Images/logo1.png" alt="Rent A Pet logo" id="logo"
         	onmouseover="document.getElementById('logo').src='Images/logo2.jpg'"
         	onmouseout="document.getElementById('logo').src='Images/logo1.png'">

    	<img src="../Images/banner.png" alt="Rent A Pet banner" id="banner">

    	<nav>
        	<a href="../Home.html">Home</a>
        	<a href="../AboutUs.html">About Us</a>
        	<a href="../Tributes.html">Tributes</a>
    	</nav>
    </header>

    <section>
        <article>
			<!-- TemplateBeginEditable name="PageContent" -->
          <h1>Welcome to Rent A Pet</h1>
          <p> Welcome to Rent A Pet! If you love to interact with pets like we do, you should enjoy
            looking around this site. Take a look at our Pet Profiles and take the opportunity to
            complete our survey. </p>
        <!-- TemplateEndEditable -->
		</article>
		
		<h2>Featured Pets Gallery</h2>

<div id="gallery">
    <div id="thumbs">
        <img src="../Images/Pet1.jpg" alt="Pet thumbnail 1"
             onmouseover="swapImage('Images/fullsize/Pet/Pet1Lg.jpg')">

        <img src="../Images/HamsterSm.jpg" alt="Pet thumbnail 2"
             onmouseover="swapImage('Images/fullsize/Pet/HamsterLg.jpg')">

        <img src="../Images/GermanShephard2Small.jpg" alt="Pet thumbnail 3"
             onmouseover="swapImage('Images/fullsize/Pet/GermanShephard2Lg.jpg')">

        <img src="../Images/CatandDogSm.jpg" alt="Pet thumbnail 4"
             onmouseover="swapImage('Images/fullsize/Pet/CatandDogLg.jpg')">
    </div>

    <div id="image">
        <img src="../Images/fullsize/Pet/Pet1Lg.jpg" alt="Full-size featured pet" id="fullsize">
    </div>
</div>
		
		<h2>Mini Tribute</h2>

<div class="tribute">
    <img src="../Images/GermanShephard1.jpg" alt="Tribute pet image" class="tributeimg">

    <p>
        One of our favorite pets is a loyal German Shephard named Max. Max is known for his
        gentle personality, playful spirit, and ability to make everyone around him smile.
        His loving nature reminds us why pets become such important members of our families.
        <a href="../Tributes.html">more &gt;&gt;</a>
    </p>
</div>
    </section>

    <footer>
    	<p><a href="mailto:10873730@uvu.edu">Webmaster Email</a></p>
    	<p>This web site has been created solely for educational purposes.</p>
	</footer>

</div>

</body>
</html>